<h1>Community Guidelines</h1>
<p>
    To maintain a healthy and productive community, please adhere to the following guidelines when posting or commenting:
</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Relevance:</strong> Ensure your posts are related to game design, development, art, audio, or the business of games.</li>
    <li><strong>Civility:</strong> Treat other members with respect. Harassment, hate speech, and personal attacks will not be tolerated.</li>
    <li><strong>No spam:</strong> Do not post spam or excessive self-promotion.</li>
    <li><strong>No clickbait:</strong> Avoid titles that are designed to generate clicks at the expense of accuracy or relevance.</li>
    <li><strong>Original sources:</strong> Whenever possible, link to the original source of an article or announcement.</li>
</ul>
<p>
    We reserve the right to remove any content that violates these guidelines.
</p>
